::KitKat::

Her head broke the surface of the water. "I can't find Quickstrike!"
She caught her breath and went down again.  She pawed around but 
still couldn't find him.  She came back up and loked at the shore.  
She dog paddled to the edge of the pool and walked out.  She layed 
down on the ground a little out of breath. She said in a low and 
dissapointed voice, "I couldn't find him. I'm sorry, I couldn't find 
him." She closed her eyes and put her ears back against her head.
